## Additional Terms for Assets

This license applies to the code and structure of the game. Individual assets 
(images, sounds, etc.) may have their own licenses. Please check the attribution 
sections in README.md for specific asset licenses.

When contributing assets, ensure they are:
- Licensed under Creative Commons, Public Domain, or MIT-compatible licenses
- Properly attributed in the project documentation
- Free for commercial and derivative use

